{"tid":2205703,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國經濟差 欲吞併港資","createTime":"2020-09-17T04:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T03:42:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":236,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"3a71d0f394a6138e71e31f272763ca92995184fc","tid":2205703,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:02:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200917/SFINSP6KBZEIFBVS3W6AG77RQM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200917%2FSFINSP6KBZEIFBVS3W6AG77RQM%2F&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BgogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=6b03b623\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200917%2FSFINSP6KBZEIFBVS3W6AG77RQM%2F&h=28fbc406\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200917/SFINSP6KBZEIFBVS3W6AG77RQM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中國經濟差 欲吞併港資<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/A7emTzjguPkmie57PbCNDKOsSJ0=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TV5JSHLGOFECHPVEHBZCDKT5ZM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FA7emTzjguPkmie57PbCNDKOsSJ0%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTV5JSHLGOFECHPVEHBZCDKT5ZM.jpg&h=84a094f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中共要求港商也要用習思想武裝頭腦。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】時事評論員劉銳紹對本報形容，香港從「黃花閨女」變了「黃臉婆」，今時不同往日，若要在內地經商只得「硬食」，港商本身優越的地位變得與內地民企一樣，情況已經有如局部共產。中共這次推出《關於加強新時代民營經濟統戰工作的意見》，很大原因是中國經濟下滑，需要吞併民企、港資。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n形同「金蛋」 貢獻8.5萬億<br />\n<br />\n「在國家改革開放進程中，港澳所處的地位是獨特的，港澳同胞所作出的貢獻是重大的，所發揮的作用是不可替代的。」習近平兩年前在北京接見港澳慶祝改革開放40周年活動代表團時這樣說。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，港資一直是內地的主要外資投資者，單是2018年，香港在內地新設立的企業就接近四萬家，涉及使用香港資金899億美元。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n對於未來港商要在內地通行，是否必定要順服共產黨，甚至成為黨員，劉銳紹指。。。。。"},{"pid":"ea3465f63a7bf0f0021165321d4753f86fcf55c7","tid":2205703,"uid":77196,"like":217,"dislike":2,"score":215,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:05:38.000Z","msg":"回血劍，國家有難，你班商家佬係時候進貢喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b02fe2da09432fa2bb0a3dd17d4bdd786ace9a","tid":2205703,"uid":25601,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"走 快走"},{"pid":"fe81679543264c8edcbe657a2b024ee7ad79fcbd","tid":2205703,"uid":27946,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:12:47.000Z","msg":"回血時間又到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553e43c77de352df4c7c1e9fe7cecee60b0042ed","tid":2205703,"uid":155095,"like":120,"dislike":2,"score":118,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:16:06.000Z","msg":"永遠相信誠哥嘅眼光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7788817f3a483ca10cbcda18dfcdee9391f6b4c","tid":2205703,"uid":55089,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8262eee7b9703dd709e788b5a16bf6438f45314e","tid":2205703,"uid":35814,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:21:29.000Z","msg":"就睇下班愛國商人有幾愛國先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a677641e2803c785ba84a0f6ba35b08d5179cb6","tid":2205703,"uid":331973,"like":101,"dislike":3,"score":98,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:22:15.000Z","msg":"好多商家佬藍到黑，係時候幫助國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，四大地產商，係時候供献祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d3acaf651947ffc29355a09cb32d5dd619e3ebd","tid":2205703,"uid":102078,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:22:56.000Z","msg":"